Agentic QA Autonomous Regression Tester – POC Document

Overview
Agentic QA is an autonomous regression testing solution for websites. It leverages AI and automation tools to interpret plain-English test cases, 
execute browser actions, validate results, and report outcomes—reducing manual QA effort and enabling faster releases.
